mil.emp3.api.interfaces

Interface IEditUpdateData


  • public interface IEditUpdateData
    This interface allows access to the edit update event data.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoAirControlMeasure.Attribute getChangedAttribute()
      This method return the ACM attribute that was updated.
      org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoMilSymbol.Modifier getChangedModifier()
      This method return the MilStd modifier that was updated.
      int[] getCoordinateIndexes()
      This method returns an array of indexes of coordinates affected by the update operation.
      FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum getUpdateType()
      This method return the type of update the EDIT_UPDATE event is indicating.

    • Method Detail

      • getUpdateType

        FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum getUpdateType()
        This method return the type of update the EDIT_UPDATE event is indicating.
        Returns:
        FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum

      • getCoordinateIndexes

        int[] getCoordinateIndexes()
        This method returns an array of indexes of coordinates affected by the update operation.
        Returns:
        An array of indexes if getUpdateType return FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum.COORDINATE_ADDED, COORDINATE_MOVED, or COORDINATE_DELETED. See @see FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum.

      • getChangedModifier

        org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoMilSymbol.Modifier getChangedModifier()
        This method return the MilStd modifier that was updated. This only applies to MilStd features.
        Returns:
        IGeoMilSymbol.Modifier enumerated value if getUpdateType return FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum.MILSTD_MODIFIER_UPDATED}, null otherwise.

      • getChangedAttribute

        org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoAirControlMeasure.Attribute getChangedAttribute()
        This method return the ACM attribute that was updated. This only applies to ACM features.
        Returns:
        IGeoAirControlMeasure.Attribute enumerated value if getUpdateType return FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum.ACM_ATTRIBUTE_UPDATED, null otherwise.
